00:45.375 --> 00:48.500
NO, WE HAVE TO STOP
DOING THIS. IT'S WRONG.

00:48.500 --> 00:49.708
YES. DEAD WRONG.

00:49.708 --> 00:51.166
PACEY.

00:51.166 --> 00:53.458
