AS SOON AS POSSIBLE,

01:19.625 --> 01:22.291
BECAUSE THE LONGER
WE WAIT, JO,
THE WORSE IT GETS.

01:22.291 --> 01:24.083
NO, PACEY.

01:24.083 --> 01:25.417
I'VE TRIED.

01:25.417 --> 01:26.583
