I SEE THE GUY NOW,
I JUST FEEL LIKE--

01:29.208 --> 01:31.708
YOU DON'T HAVE TO BOTHER
FILLING IN THE EXPLETIVE, OK?

01:31.708 --> 01:35.250
I MEAN, THIS ISN'T
EXACTLY THE EASIEST THING
I'VE EVER HAD TO DO, PACEY--

01:35.250 --> 01:37.583
