AND I CAN'T STOP
THINKING ABOUT HIM

01:42.959 --> 01:44.583
OR WANTING TO BE NEAR HIM

01:44.583 --> 01:46.792
OR WANTING TO KISS HIM
ALL THE TIME.

01:54.208 --> 01:55.625
