IS ONE DAY.

02:15.625 --> 02:16.291
JUST ONE DAY.

02:21.542 --> 02:22.500
ONE DAY.

02:22.500 --> 02:23.917
YES.

02:23.917 --> 02:25.542
ONE DAY.

